<html>
	<head>
		<title>Password Reset</title>
		<style>
			body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f4f4f4; color: #333; line-height: 1.6; } .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0
			auto; padding: 20px; background: #fff; border: 1px solid #ddd; } .buttonContainer { text-align: center; } .button { display: inline-block;
			padding: 10px 20px; margin: 20px 0; background: #0056b3; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; } .footer { text-align:
			center; font-size: 0.8em; color: #666; }
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<div class="container">
			<h2>Password Reset</h2>
			<p>Hello {{username}},</p>
			<p>
				You have requested to reset your password. Please click on the link below to set a new password. This link will expire in 30 minutes.
			</p>
			<div class="buttonContainer">
				<a href={{resetLink}} class="button">Reset My Password</a>
			</div>
			<p>If you did not request a password reset, please ignore this email.</p>
			<div class="footer">
				<p>Regards,</p>
				<p>The Jyogames Team</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>